          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">Tested booking flows. Site A: "Call to book" (leave voicemail, wait 24+ hours). Site B: integrated Booking.com calendar, one-tap reservation from phone (3 screens to confirm). Result: Site B got 77% more bookings. Modern couples: search on phone during wine tasting, want instant confirmation. They don't leave voicemail. They book the inn with mobile-friendly calendar.</p>
